  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;white-space-collapse:collapse;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-shadow:transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27.2px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n    <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n     <div data-id=\"85660\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n      <div data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; text-decoration: inherit; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em 0px 0px;padding: 0.5em 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n       <p mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: -1.2em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font-family: inherit; border-width: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 29.75px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-align: center;font-family: inherit;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:15px;line-height:29.75px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgb(117, 117, 118);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;font-family:inherit;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">机器之心报道</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">机器之心编辑部</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">经常使用 AI 的人，大概都注意到模型一个共同特点，那就是它们非常喜欢用破折号。无论是解释概念、列举观点，还是自然过渡语气，动不动就来一个「——」。久而久之，它甚至成了检测 AI 文本的土办法之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">举几个例子，我们随手让 ChatGPT 翻译一段英文，短短两句话，结果里竟然冒出了两个「——」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518330\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11388888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1212\" data-height=\"138\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ec0d996&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hBOkkH7aV8ccycwqHlngw5Rpl23r1dZ6f935wfOdIOticHAQ6EBTTaicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">介绍一篇文章主旨，写着写着，又莫名其妙地冒出了好几个「——」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"381\" data-imgfileid=\"503518331\" data-ratio=\"0.30185185185185187\" data-width=\"1263\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=105cfd5e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4he46iaJZJUG1icw7wsiaGviaKBlwicC8vTckhrwckkhF8t91MyzPN7VWqvzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">久而久之，这种习惯就被人戏称为ChatGPT 体，只要文本里破折号用得特别勤快，大家第一反应就是：好嘛，这又是 AI 写的吧？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">于是，一个有趣的现象出现了，本来只是普通的标点符号，却突然成了判别AI的标准。哪怕作者根本没用任何 AI，只是单纯觉得破折号读起来顺口，也很可能被大家误判为机器写作。久而久之，大家开始戒备起来，能不用就不用，能换掉就换掉，生怕一个不留神，就让文章误以为是机器写的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518332\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2932692307692308\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"624\" data-width=\"624\" data-height=\"183\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6e40afbd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hIKSfqWo0Y3jFGHvQzNHv6er02YY1NnRUFSKH5CBxRDNKjU3ZsZTXPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518333\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25283630470016205\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"617\" data-width=\"617\" data-height=\"156\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a892cd8e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hxdUia7wqz7smAXctewyRI2UHrHBwE3fziaN2oOY9t0rhth55ZlgTvbhw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518334\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25365853658536586\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"615\" data-width=\"615\" data-height=\"156\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f7a52fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hnrbXWmias3kBZ44aC5EtUpLLhTLiaoDg7NgSiaC5ictpBHWJ9gy6ehlibibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">现在ChatGPT这个令人头大的问题，终于被解决了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">刚刚，OpenAI CEO Sam Altman 表示他们已经解决了这一问题：「如果你在自定义指令里告诉 ChatGPT 不要使用破折号『Do not use em dashes』，它终于会乖乖照做了。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Altman将这一更新称为一个「很小但令人开心的胜利」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518335\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4447852760736196\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"978\" data-width=\"978\" data-height=\"435\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=119a7d09&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hA5a86v36IE4hkliam8fP775pgiceRPyAicCuCtso8SdjGGn6OQRjEsBHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过，Altman评论区很快被攻陷：「（根据指令照做了）破折号依然存在」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518336\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1580547112462006\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"987\" data-width=\"987\" data-height=\"156\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c85c9173&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4h5eklDuUBEUIex2qrKxIic9nibj91WNDJzacGKf5rDA74fJAMu5QHw7cA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">前脚让它不要用破折号，ChatGPT 转头又冒了出来，让人觉得有点哭笑不得。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518337\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7940267765190525\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"971\" data-width=\"971\" data-height=\"771\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a772536&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hBLicqTeWBFt8E8hudsicMCVX9A5giaVEibgfUFpibEd9pd1icrWNYlpVZBqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们随后亲自测试了前面提到的例子，结果发现 ChatGPT 在收到「Do not use em dashes」指令后，回复中并没有出现破折号。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518338\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25833333333333336\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1497\" data-height=\"387\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3a3fd79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hYcbmaYGWzHxLBFYfibhnRNic16Ur7oG1VbtbrAOCcEpicrPG58jTO0snA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518339\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6083333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1499\" data-height=\"912\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67e0ad25&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hOtdxjrdmDGf5oJPKiaicdGyRxFt1AktPq2F35vQibaeyDuoBfN1DXVN8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">感兴趣的读者，也可以测试一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">除了破折号，AI还喜欢用这些</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">除了破折号，一些看似无害的英文也开始频繁出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518340\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5023923444976076\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"627\" data-width=\"627\" data-height=\"315\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66319c7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hMmVEvOCuw3eSl3HMpjibsbPytbyTLZZ2YJLMJooKAuRFdibzGVYZalhQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">例如，模型在解释一段话时，经常出现这种情况：名词（英文），如波函数（wave function）。其实英文并没有必要写出来，尤其是在语境已经完全明确的情况下。通篇看下来，这种情况还不少。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518341\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4962962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1239\" data-height=\"615\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=705a1d7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4h6iauRct8pb7DC9wNZ3HU5zqc3XtCbNtLD6uV3ByonQefGeBObOxqUNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「“”」也是随处可见，只要遇到稍微抽象一点的词语，它就会主动把它们引（“”）起来，好像在提醒读者这是一个特别概念。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518342\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.19907407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1217\" data-height=\"242\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eaccd91d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hzNp557myXGFXEQYNTBIaKy3JwibE3IoRPib4Yb8MXia3R2BZ6V7729VEA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其实，这些 AI 特有的标记并不会真正影响模型输出的内容。在一些人看来，比如破折号能够提升表达效率，能够让句子更紧凑，也算得上一种优点。只是当全文读下来，如果某些符号使用得过于频繁，整体观感就会受到影响，就会产生这是AI写的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518343\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3027375201288245\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"621\" data-width=\"621\" data-height=\"188\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69798140&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hY6CSMj6SO7rRV6hFTlfia6oia374w2MTceusckCQa8RTR7zp5vxAs2UA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就像这位网友说的，原本自己喜欢用破折号，有了AI以来就算是自己写的看起来也不像了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518344\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30434782608695654\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"621\" data-width=\"621\" data-height=\"189\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2b7beed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW87uG1DXQdp9SfJSLDribs4hVoDolKtSn9Bydbmt3VPFvWgGHaTkVwdNX8d6lJGRHSFY4D5o3dAHxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">你还遇到过AI哪些「痕迹」，欢迎评论区留言。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章探讨了 ChatGPT 过度使用破折号等标点和表达习惯，及其对用户体验和 AI 文本识别的影响，并验证了 OpenAI 通过自定义指令解决此问题的有效性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章探讨了 ChatGPT 过度使用破折号等标点和表达习惯，及其对用户体验和 AI 文本识别的影响，并验证了 OpenAI 通过自定义指令解决此问题的有效性。",
  "summary": "文章指出，ChatGPT 等大型 AI 模型在生成文本时普遍存在过度使用破折号的习惯，这一现象甚至使其成为一种非官方的 AI 文本识别特征，并给人类作者带来了困扰。OpenAI CEO Sam Altman 曾宣布已通过自定义指令“Do not use em dashes”解决了这一问题，尽管初期用户反馈不一，但机器之心团队的实测证实了该指令的有效性。此外，文章还提及了 AI 其他常见的写作习惯，如在中文文本中冗余地标注英文原词和过度使用引号，并探讨了这些风格对文本观感和人类写作感知的影响，强调了 AI 输出风格控制的重要性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "ChatGPT 过度使用破折号已成为其显著特征，甚至被用作 AI 文本识别的非官方方法。",
      "explanation": "AI 模型频繁的破折号使用习惯不仅使其生成文本易于辨识，也影响了人类作者的写作，使其担忧自己的作品被误判为 AI 生成。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 已提供通过自定义指令控制 ChatGPT 输出风格的能力，并经实测验证有效，以解决破折号滥用问题。",
      "explanation": "Sam Altman 宣布用户可以通过“Do not use em dashes”指令有效控制 ChatGPT 不再使用破折号，文章实测也验证了这一解决方案的可行性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "除了破折号，AI 还存在其他影响文本观感的写作习惯，如冗余的英文括号和过度使用引号。",
      "explanation": "这些看似细微的风格问题，虽然不影响内容本身，但频繁出现会降低文本的阅读体验，并进一步强化 AI 写作的“痕迹”，值得关注。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "经常使用 AI 的人，大概都注意到模型一个共同特点，那就是它们非常喜欢用破折号。",
    "久而久之，这种习惯就被人戏称为 ChatGPT 体，只要文本里破折号用得特别勤快，大家第一反应就是：好嘛，这又是 AI 写的吧？",
    "如果你在自定义指令里告诉 ChatGPT 不要使用破折号『Do not use em dashes』，它终于会乖乖照做了。",
    "就像这位网友说的，原本自己喜欢用破折号，有了 AI 以来就算是自己写的看起来也不像了。"
  ],
